For popular comedian, Itoto Bartholomew popularly called Hon. Madiba, the month of February remains an ever-busy and historic one, as he continues his United Kingdom tour show tagged ‘Madiba Updated’. Madiba who is billed to tour major cities of Manchester, Birmingham, London among others has promised bumper laughter and entertainment for his expectant fans. Against the storm and unfriendly weather condition, the Manchester edition which took place at popular Bulgarry Event Center, Longsight, Friday, was indeed a total shutdown, with so much glamour in the air and the delighted fans asking for more. Clearly, they can’t wait for the next stop of ‘Madiba Updated’   The Voice Nigeria returns for season 4 as FirstBank…     Steve Gukas’ Cake goes to cinemas     I don’t see anything wrong with two adults recording…   Hon. Madiba is performing alongside big names in the Nigerian comedy industry like Homeoflafta, Allamano, Privilege Son, Don Nice among others. - Advertisement - He will be rounding off the international tour with a huge show in Istanbul, Turkey. Despite the lull currently being experienced in the entertainment industry in Africa, Hon. Madiba is motivated to making the show most talked about. For the home fans, he has promised an exciting homecoming show come April in Benin City. SPONSORED